snippet.title: LET'S PLAY SUPER MARIO RPG 2 (PART 1)
snippet.description: My gameplay of Super Mario RPG 2: Legend of the Five Pendants.  This is a fan game which I found challenging and yet fun!  It's no Super Mario RPG: Legend of the Seven Stars, but still entertaining in my opinion.  Thanks for watching!
